#MOBILES
#17000
spectator battle cave~
A spectator~
A battle cave spectator is here, cheering for the combatants.
~
The sound this man is making in front of you is deafening. He screams
at the top of his lungs for his favorite combatant. He totally
ignores any advice given by the other spectators to keep his voice down
and continues to scream in your ear. He stands wearing a nice blue
baseball cap and a pair of nice looking gray trousers.
~
