gambler battle cave~
A gambler~
A battle cave gambler is here, waving money in your face.
~
This man stands very firm in his seat while he waves frantically a
money clip filled with bills. Judging by the clothing this man is
wearing, you can tell that he isn't one in the unemployment lines.
He pushes you out the way as you block his view of the ring.
