#17002
white suit guard~
A security guard~
A guard dressed in a white suit is here, supervising the fight.
~
This man wears a nice pair of shades and holds a portable phone in his
right hand. He glances at your presence and begins to follow your
movements with his eyes. You can tell that this man isn't going to let
out of his sight. He tells you to hurry along and scoots you away from
him.
~
