#17003
dhamd champion~
Dhamd~
Dhamd sits in his corner, awaiting the bell to ring.
~
Dhamd is a man built like a god. Looks like this man has gone through
months and months of training to where he is right now. He sits
calmly in his corner, awaiting the bell to ring for round one. Dhamd,
defending champion of the Battle Cave, glances at you and begins to
snicker softly as the bell rings.
~
Human~
