#17004
egis~
Egis~
Egis stands firmly against his corner, awaiting the fight.
~
Egis looks like he could weigh more than 5 mac trucks. This man has so
much body weight that the ring begins to slightly shake as he takes steps
to his corner. He glares at Dhamd, his opponent, and then at you. He
begins to burst out in laughter as his eyes leave you. Wonder what he
was thinking about.
~
