black suit guard huge man~
An elite bodyguard~
A huge man wearing a black suit stands mocking you.
~
The bodyguard stands firmly as he pushes you out of this area. He begins
to mock you, telling you to leave unless you like getting your a$$ kicked.
His black suit is finely made from a well-known designer and the
jewelry he wears on his neck and wrist is genuine gold. The idea of you
leaving comes across your head as he begins to walk rapidly towards you.
~
